text: Aranka Szeiler (5 May 1909 - 31 January 1982) was a Hungarian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1909 births Category:1982 deaths Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Budapest
